entries.title_d: Intercept the Eliminator in space and destroy him. When you complete this mission, return to Sergeant Rhea in Coronet and Sergeant Rhea will train you in a new Pilot skill.
entries.title: Corellia System: Destroy the Hidden Dagger Eliminator
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: \#pcontrast3 Sgt Rhea: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and hunt that Eliminator down. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Sgt Rhea: < \#pcontrast1 You appear to have hit a little snag out there Captain.  Get patched up and hunt that Eliminator down. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_target_d: One of the Hidden Dagger Sub-bosses
entries.quest_escort_d: Hidden Dagger Enforcers, not a priority target.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 The mark has escaped, you have failed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 An escorting craft has been destroyed, %DI remain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 We need that escort eliminated as well Captain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 The Eliminator is dead, good work. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 Upload complete, good luck Captain. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 CorSec Command: < \#pcontrast1 We are uploading the location of his last known position. \#pcontrast3 >
